settings.subtitle: Early Season
settings.title: Verdigre Series
settings.text: the most versatile gear we have in the line. The full "Fleece-Wool" construction makes this series the right choice for active scenarios and covering ground to and from the stand.

settings.title: Zone7-Versa Series
settings.text: We built this line to adapt to both the lower and upper end temperatures of the midwest in peak rut. Construction of this series was designed for ideal movement and shooting function.

settings.text: All of the warmth, minimal bulk thanks to our layering system found in these garments.
